}"},"$:/plugins/rimir/file-pipeline/prompts/tender-highlights":{"title":"$:/plugins/rimir/file-pipeline/prompts/tender-highlights","tags":"$:/tags/rimir/file-pipeline/prompt","type":"text/vnd.tiddlywiki","caption":"Tender Highlights","description":"Analyze tender document and highlight noteworthy sections","text":"You are analyzing a tender document. Your task is to:

